OL,3,CNottingham Forest docked four points
OL,4,Cfor breaching Premier League rules
OL,6,FTheir latest result was a 1-1 draw
OL,7,Fagainst Luton Town on Saturday 16th
OL,8,FMarch.
OL,10,FBefore the match, the sides were only
OL,11,Fseparated by 3 points, with the
OL,12,FHatters sat below Forest in the
OL,13,Frelegation zone.
OL,15,FNuno called the match a "must-win"
OL,16,Fgame but despite being given the lead
OL,17,Fthrough Chris Wood in the 34th minute,
OL,18,FForest had to share the points after
OL,19,FLuke Berry smashed in an equaliser.
